{"tid":2226314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"親密幕僚確診武漢肺炎  川普：我與梅蘭妮亞將開始進行隔離","createTime":"2020-10-02T03:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T03:40:40.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4cde4e6e705248231efc2eccc94d2080bb86a4","tid":2226314,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普的親密幕僚希克斯（Hope Hicks）1日確診武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19），川普證實這項消息，並稱自己與夫人梅蘭妮亞都已進行病毒檢測，正在等待結果，且兩人已進入隔離程序。<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》 報導，川普在美東時間1日晚間接受《福斯新聞》主持人韓尼提（Sean Hannity）電話訪問時證實，他的高級顧問希克斯確診武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n川普也在推特上表示，「一直努力工作沒休息的希克斯確診了武漢肺炎，實在太糟糕了！我和第一夫人都在等待我們的檢測結果，同時我們將開始隔離程序！」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n《路透》 報導，希克斯經常與川普搭乘空軍一號移動，希克斯在9月29日陪同川普參加在位於俄亥俄州的總統辯論會，並在9月29日一同前往明尼蘇達州參加競選活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3309569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309569&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=a700c902\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309569&h=e7cf0c3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3309569</a>"},{"pid":"37c6a96ceaa611909ace581e36a155a0883eb64d","tid":2226314,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚係掛"},{"pid":"918bf4e3883fd49137efb8ed0b01bdad7d613889","tid":2226314,"uid":59617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"china joe 同個日個主持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/